Quantum computing is basically about processing information simultaneously. That said, we’re playing with numerous unknowns and the main technology has been kept from the public. Origin Pilot is the first major step towards changing that in a meaningful way. It’s important to note that parts of this video oversimplify concepts to make them digestible. For instance, observing quantum entanglement typically breaks the entanglement - it’s more about the identification of the phenomenon that is so “spooky” and fascinating.
